Big.

7
00:01:39,958 --> 00:01:40,791
Li Jingnian.

8
00:01:40,958 --> 00:01:42,333
If you keep guessing like this,

9
00:01:42,458 --> 00:01:44,291
Xu Luohan will lose his life.

10
00:01:50,625 --> 00:01:51,625
